  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc5 \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dba\u0dd4\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dda \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0dc5\u0db9\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0da7\u0dad\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Further turbulence in the lower atmosphere",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Meteorology, due to the turbulent nature of the lower atmosphere surrounding the island, thundershowers of around 150 mm may occur in many parts of the island.",
        "The announcement of the Department of Meteorology states that in some places of the Western, Southern, Sabaragamuwa, Central and Uva provinces, a heavy rainfall of about 150 mm may be recorded and in other provinces of the island, heavy rain may exceed 100 mm.",
        "Due to the possible rainy weather conditions, the people living in landslide prone areas should be concerned about the possible risk and if any landslide pre-characteristics are observed, the disaster management center is requested to inform the people. Also, the people in the flood-prone areas of the river valleys are requested to take measures to protect their property from the risk of flooding.",
        "In case of thunderstorms, avoid being outdoors or under trees to avoid lightning accidents, go to a safe building or a closed vehicle and stay safe, don't stay in open places such as paddy fields, playgrounds or ponds, ponds, reservoirs, wired telephones, electric The Disaster Management Center advises people to follow safety measures such as avoiding the use of appliances, unplugging electrical appliances, and avoiding the use of open vehicles such as bicycles, tractors, motorcycles or boats.",
        "It is also requested to take action to minimize the damage that may occur due to the falling of dangerous trees and power lines and to know about the current weather conditions or to provide information about the distressing conditions caused by any disaster, call the emergency number 117 of the Disaster Management Center is there"
      ],
